data.description: Perched on the hill and nestled under the Oak trees, this unique Truland home is fresh and clean and ready for it's new owner. Custom cabinets, granite, Bosch appliances including 5 burner gas cook top and center island great for entertaining. Hand scraped wood floors, extensive tile and granite in all baths, fireplace with custom mantle. Spacious primary bath with huge walk in closet. Beautiful front and back porches with stained pine ceilings. Unique Truland floor plan with primary wing on one end, grand foyer and dining room in the middle and kitchen and living area on the other end of the house. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, plenty of room to spread out. Large fenced backyard
